CGUNITID - Institution ID (IPEDSID) of comparison institution
IPEDS ID of each comparison institution in the custom comparison group submitted by the institution for use in the 2018 IPEDS Data Feedback Report (DFR). When using the by groups option to select instititutions in the Data Center, the custom comparison group is referenced as the "Saved group" and the comparison group created by NCES is referenced as the "Automatic group".
Format
Data type:N
Field width:6
Variable format:Cont
Variable number:16001

Source
Var source:IPEDS, 2017-18 collection system
File title:Institutional Characteristics
Section title:Institutional Characteristics
Table name:CUSTOMCGIDS2017

CGSTABBR - State abbreviation of comparison institution
Identifies the State locations (abbreviation) of each comparison institution in the custom comparison group submitted by the institution for use in the 2018 IPEDS Data Feedback Report (DFR). When using the by groups option to select instititutions in t he Data Center, the custom comparison group is referenced as the "Saved group" and the comparison group created by NCES is referenced as the "Automatic group".
